  "text": "(154) This recovers the fractional reaction-diffusion equation derived from the diffusion limit of continuous time random walks in [CITATION_1] . We note that this is a potentially non-linear equation as a(x, t) and c(x, t) may be dependent on the concentration u(x, t).",
